548
00:46:20,000 --> 00:46:23,073
Saya ingin berbual sedikit dengannya.

549
00:46:23,073 --> 00:46:26,147
Bawa pulang Solar! Sekarang!

550
00:46:26,147 --> 00:46:27,713
- Pergi!
- Solar!

551
00:46:28,473 --> 00:46:29,493
Sun, mari kita pergi!

552
00:46:29,493 --> 00:46:30,773
apa?

553
00:46:32,473 --> 00:46:35,000
Saya tidak boleh bangun. Tolong saya.

554
00:46:35,000 --> 00:46:36,360
[Baucar Ciuman - 1 ciuman/jam]

